n remain necessary after generation.\",\n    \"SLF4J may log warnings without a binding, but a binding is not required for meaningful coverage or normal test execution.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08867fb52bb5ba31016a425c1656688197af97549712affdc5\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1334, "output": 508, "cacheRead": 40960, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 42802, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782733838999, "responseId": "resp_08867fb52bb5ba31016a425c0fd0288197ab7a1c4f6c5514b3"}}
